txt.en: The army gathered within Madh-fushaum is mostly comprised of ragtag Dunlendings, but they are mingled with Orcs and Uruk-hai. You should defeat as many as possible.
The army gathered within Madh-fushaum is mostly comprised of ragtag Dunlendings, but they are mingled with Orcs and Uruk-hai. You should defeat as many as possible.
There are far too many of the enemy gathered in Madh-fushaum for one to handle alone. However, those that remain will never forget the day the you stepped foot in Madh-fushaum.
You have left a mark upon those that remain in Madh-fushaum, having seen their fellows soundly defeated. You took them by surprise, and they will not soon forget this day.
The army that built and now resides within Madh-fushaum has destroyed Flodgeheld and is responsible for the attacks and siege on Brockbridge. The time has come to go on the offensive.
The army gathered within Madh-fushaum is mostly comprised of ragtag Dunlendings, but they are mingled with Orcs and Uruk-hai. You should defeat as many as possible.
